<p>We received a request to reset your password. If you made this request, please follow the link below to reset your password</p>

<p><%= link_to "Reset your password", @url, class: 'btn' %></p>

<p>Or copy and paste the following link into your browser if you are unable to click the link:</p>
<pre class="break-all"><%= @url %></pre>

